Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得什麼地方不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道為什麼 但我就是這樣覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}請看………
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:25.80,Black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz17.94\c&H000000&\pos(562,362)}來電 涼宮春日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 今天閒著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午二點 準時 咖啡館集合 完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還什麼都沒說呢 完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了說 不要忘記帶上你的全套泳裝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假才過一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假作業的話 後面有的是時間做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(952,594)}不會完結的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露天泳池…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天果然還是泳池最爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要玩兒個盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日 暑假一到你這句台詞聽得我耳朵都起繭子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 大繭子上面再加一層 然後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太得意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繭子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 泳池是禁止跳入的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 剛才你看見了 我是被踢下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 進入泳池之前不好好做熱身操是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 你總是在泳裝活動中出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始進行障礙跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個到達終點的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有權利隨便吃這些美味的水果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榴蓮 香瓜 芒果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是和實久留一起品嚐喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香瓜 香瓜 香瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害的高級水果 多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要開始了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咚~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~~不敢往前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我覺得比起妹妹來香瓜更有吸引力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒~~~~榴蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉桑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日喵和阿虛的激烈競爭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 香瓜桑 為了朝比奈的話 無論哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡 眼鏡 眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此我也必須繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到手啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！香瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 你好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果大家都可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香瓜 在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦··謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有櫻桃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這麼黃暴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:00:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 作業寫完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎~不過總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 正好今晚有盂蘭盆舞大會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都會參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上浴衣 在車站前集合喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日 我··
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那五點集合喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒~有點難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實久留醬 腰 腰動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈穿浴衣的樣子賽高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 現在不是撒歡的時候 我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這次是兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}請多關照 請一定看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個弄完之後 接著是上貨喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明在吃冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 作業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒做完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~再不做就不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春日 今天我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天體觀測大會喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望遠鏡的話就我這邊來準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是鶴屋學姐 這樣就好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的天氣很好 一定能看到美麗的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 今天的天體觀測大會一定要找到火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實久留也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}誒！火星人 火星人 火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 要是找不到做作業的時間的話…·
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去釣魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說春日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 阿虛 你難道打算把釣到的魚吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣到的魚 Catch and release
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與大自然共存共息 佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…·作業 作業 作業 作業 作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間了 大家趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快 接下來是懸疑片喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝倉學姐 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說長門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 還沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得再不做的話就真糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一定要給春日提議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一整天作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 春日 今天··
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~~~~鬥志滿滿 阿虛 不要磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 就是想磨磨蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去K歌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah 個毛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說阿虛 怎麼今天一臉衰樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個··春日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們去觀察野鳥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼著都行隨你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大自然果然好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 非常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說長門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假還有兩天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假馬上就完了 你的作業寫完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑呢 涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業什麼的七月就應該做完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按照日程表來安排 八月初就做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…總之 課題到現在算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這些的話夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 大家還有其他什麼想做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 這個夏天很多心願也算是完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 今天就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一整天都沒安排
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣睡一天也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後天 部門活動室碰面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的作業還沒有做完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
