Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打牌的話不想太動腦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去的話要受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就決定玩大貧民了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽烏龜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大貧民！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能玩一會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事要有度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H3823EE&\pos(1044,566)}第24場對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 有沒有讓涼子成為大富豪的分牌方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 臣妾實在是做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虛 想想辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話去跟朝倉說 不要跟我這個無法擺脫貧民的人說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有要說的話也是跟每次都是大富豪的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:21:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 想辦法讓朝倉變大富豪 讓這場無休止的遊戲結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 那應該怎麼辦才可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 這回誰不看氣氛 當上大富豪 誰就要接受懲♂罰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒 大富豪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古泉好像說 finish 了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門本來就是一晚上就能搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我沒做完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長門嗎 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.93,0:22:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我去你那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作業 幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.10,0:22:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我抄下吧 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在剛剛做完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.69,0:22:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等你哦

